          <p class="MB_Body"><p>Had a blinding Easter Monday, killed a few uber Mobs, and actually got to pull for the first time in ages. I have slightly modified a child&#8217;s rhyme to indicate what happened (as if anyone is in any doubt)

<p>Rumblecrush says, &#8216;I saw a Bodi!&#8217; <br>
Rumblecrush iniates a FLURRY of attacks on You!<br>

a massive stone elemental guardian says, &#8216;Where?&#8217;<br>

Rumblecrush hits You! For 720 damage!<br>

Rumblecrush says, &#8216;There on the stairs, there on the stairs, right there!&#8217;
<br>
Rumblecrush hits You! For 720 damage!<br>

Rumblecrush says, &#8216;A little Bodi with clogs on&#8217;
<br>
Rumblecrush hits You! For 720 damage!<br>

Rumblecrush says, &#8216;Well I declare, going clip clippity clop on the stairs&#8217;
<br>
Rumblecrush hits You! For 720 damage!<br>

You have been slain by Rumblecrush!<br>


<p>And to add a last word or two, I will paraphrase one of my all time favourite films, which sums up my feelings here over the last few days (other than being a tad angry)

<p>"&#8230;..and just like that, he was gone."
</p>
